                                    konungs ens helga</ref>
                                <biblScope unit="page">193-96</biblScope>
                            </bibl>
                            <bibl>Johnsen og Jón Helgason: <ref type="primary-3" target="OlHJH">Den
                                    store saga om Olav den Hellige</ref>
